    "body": "I'm sorry, but importing from the parent path is not supported like that, because it would not be possible to generate a virtual directory structure to be used internally by the compiler. Please use remappings (and import from global virtual paths) or restructure your code layout so that this is not required.\r\n\r\nCreated an issue to track documentation: https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/4915",
